g real-time metrics), (3) the measurable outcome with specific metrics (percentages, dollar amounts, time savings), (4) the business impact explaining how this transformed operations or customer experience. Example format: 'AI-Driven Fraud Detection & Prevention - I architected an automated Fraud Detection Pipeline using n8n and Azure OpenAI to analyze call transcripts for social engineering patterns in real-time. By cross-referencing caller metadata with Pinecone vector embeddings of known fraud tactics, I improved detection speed by 15%. This system balanced a frictionless customer experience with rigorous security protocols, significantly de-risking contact centre operations.' Tailor all 5 project themes specifically to the target company's industry from company_research. Include in both resume_html (h2 section with each project as h3 title + p description) and sample_projects JSON array."
    },
    {
      role: "user",
      content: "JOB ID: " + job.job_id + " JOB TITLE: " + job.title + " COMPANY: " + job.company_name + " JOB DESCRIPTION: " + desc + " COMPANY RESEARCH: " + companyResearch + " FIT: Score=" + job.fit.fit_score + " Matched=" + JSON.stringify(job.fit.matched_requirements || []) + " Missing=" + JSON.stringify(job.fit.missing_requirements || []) + " MASTER RESUME (ALL employers): " + resume
    }
  ],
  response_format: { type: "json_object" },
  max_tokens: 12000
};

return [{ json: { ...job, body_string: JSON.stringify(body) } }];
